- How to avoid data stores of temporary sessions to leak? If a renderer
  crashes, temporary session data store files won't be deleted. How to detect
  these files must be deleted and where can we do it? On the other side, if
  the all browser crashes, we can easily delete them all by removing all files
  with a `.thds' extension.
- How to avoid a persistent session to be loaded in several documents? We could
  use file locks. But we must carefully delete them and manage browser and
  renderer crashes.
